Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Arrival of autumn
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0407jhy
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 25 Sep 1977
Myths and fallacies connected to the arrival of autumn. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.